  "ticket": {
    "de": "Alle internen Netze (port1, vlan10, vlan20) sollen DNS beim DMZ-Resolver SRV_DNS01 machen dürfen. Direkt-DNS ins Internet bleibt verboten. — Netzwerkteam, das Zonen liebt.",
    "en": "All internal networks (port1, vlan10, vlan20) may do DNS against DMZ resolver SRV_DNS01. Direct DNS to the internet stays forbidden. — The network team, which loves zones."
